@startuml
actor ProductOwner
participant "Backlog System" as BacklogSystem
participant "Backlog Management Component" as BacklogComponent
database "Backlog Database" as BacklogDB

ProductOwner -> BacklogSystem : Open Backlog System
BacklogSystem -> ProductOwner : Show 'Add Backlog Item' option

ProductOwner -> BacklogSystem : Enter backlog item details
BacklogSystem -> BacklogComponent : validateAndCreateItem(details)
BacklogComponent -> BacklogDB : save(newBacklogItem)
BacklogDB --> BacklogComponent : confirmation
BacklogComponent --> BacklogSystem : success response

BacklogSystem -> ProductOwner : Show confirmation message
@enduml
